name: Nobody Knows What Happened
description: roll_01_shot_03 There is an image underneath it all. It's just nobody knows what it is, and I don't remember. The chemicals didn't react. And so the new image was born - from the scratches, the sleepy chemicals and the memories gone. // Ilford single use camera, 2018. Part of '36 shots', a series of photographs all shot on single-use cameras. @edgardubrovskiy
